help.message:
@noninteractive
*@name*, it's your very first mission: just add one planet and make it orbit around the star!


*Click "Next" to learn how.*
@proceed

@noninteractive
Your goal is to complete your mission in as little time as possible. Your current
elapsed time is shown in the top right corner.  
@proceed

@noninteractive
To review your current mission at any time, click on the @icon-help Help button!

*Now, let's start playing!*
@proceed

Awesome!  Lot of useful information about your planet is shown in the upper right, 
such as its distance from the star, its speed, and the time it takes to orbit the star.  
@proceed
